The Essential Reality P5 Data Glove Library
-------------------------------------------

Copyright 2003, Jason McMullan <jmcmulla@linuxcare.com

Introduction
------------

  The Essential Reality P5 Data Glove is a USB device that reports
5 finger positions, and 8 X/Y/Z IR locations. 


Library Features
----------------

  This library is a polling system. See demos/p5dump.c for a simple
example usage.
  
